            """
            <p data-result>Nothing</p>
            """
        Given I have a "public/cat/index.htm" file with the body:
            """
            <h1>cat index</h1>
            """
        Given I have a "public/cat/cat.html" file with the body:
            """
            <h1>cat cat</h1>
            """
